{"tid":1239113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（重要）召喚所有backup撚，文宣撚，整合撚","createTime":"2019-06-18T05:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:25:58.000Z","uid":242805,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f42a603e5985cb060b607847c0973ab6c0b8ada6","tid":1239113,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:10:47.000Z","msg":"召喚所有backup撚，文宣撚<br />\n我係一位香港人，我想出返啲力<br />\n話說我星期日發夢有人開左個網比人整合資料，點知上左去真係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkyebook.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkyebook.com%2F&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=0f66a731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkyebook.com/</a><br />\n由於佢係夢話佢只得一個人，星期日朝早開左個網之後就出左去遊行，夜晚返黎第2朝返工，夜晚放工返到去得返個幾鍾搵片po上去，佢開個網既原意係想大家一齊backup同整合所有有價值既文章、影片、照片、黑警證據、網民創作既相。<br />\n<br />\n由於佢工作過忙令到進度超級緩慢，我係度請所有backup撚一齊幫幫佢<br />\n<br />\n如果你既文章係整合文，請自己持續更新，因為只有你可以對自己既文章更新<br />\n<br />\n由於網民過多文章一定有重複，建議大家要盡量補充自己既文章內容<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要sand email到(miyoko@hkyebook.com)<br />\n內容打整合資料就可以<br />\n佢得一個人，所以回覆較慢<br />\n好快就可以收到增加發文權限既電郵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於容量唔係無限，請大家盡量用外部連結<br />\n<br />\n佢仲參考緊外國網站搵緊防止5毛3毛破壞既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我強烈建議整合撚都要加入，因為用電腦網頁版排版發文有更多編輯選項<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對於任何打狗行為，請將主人模糊，保障主人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac43e3cdb2edd2d4c802a2b5a9410f8070b3f10","tid":1239113,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba0165e942f32d32d486f009fdfaf8883fcfef93","tid":1239113,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dac43e3cdb2edd2d4c802a2b5a9410f8070b3f10","tid":1239113,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:25:40.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我.....朋友都係比自殺單野激一激先開個網<br />\n佢都好似更新，但係返工沒撚哂時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油🇭🇰🇭🇰🇭🇰"},{"pid":"56dfa76e284351d2f2a4db0b46900c472564dfdf","tid":1239113,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"佢都好想更新"}]}